<section>
  <article>
    <h2 class="heading">Consulting</h2>
    <p>Allons-y (<em>ah-lo(n)-zee</em>) is an idiomatic French expression meaning roughly, "Let's go!"</p>
    <p>That's exactly the energy this venture brings to the web. I'm looking to explore how we deliver web experiences at enterprise scale in a way that empowers developers to work in unison with each other and with their design counterparts.</p>
  </article>

  {% if projects.featured.length %}
    <article>
      {% set type = "project" %}
      {% set label = "Featured projects" %}
      {% set items = projects.featured %}
      {% include "list.njk" ignore missing %}
  </article>
  {% endif %}

  {% if projects.tooling.length %}
      {% set label = "Projects" %}
      {% set items = projects.tooling %}
      {% set simple = true %}
      <sl-details>
        {% include "list.njk" ignore missing %}
      </sl-details>
      {% set simple = false %}
  {% endif %}

  {% if videos.conferences.length %}
    <article class="wide">
      {% set label = "Presentations" %}
      {% set type = "video" %}
      {% set items = videos.conferences | reverse %}
      {% include "list.njk" ignore missing %}
    </article>
  {% endif %}
</section>